  ## 1.12.5 / 2021-09-27

  ### Security

  [JRuby] Address CVE-2021-41098 ([GHSA-2rr5-8q37-2w7h](https://github.com/sparklemotion/nokogiri/security/advisories/GHSA-2rr5-8q37-2w7h)).

